<L>__{interior castle hackton roderick's study day}
<A>__{roderick and his accountant going over the bills which he has heaped on the table.}
<C>__{roderick }
<D>__{the news of his majesty's disregard were not long in getting around, and, in a very short time, all the bills came down upon me together all the bills i had been contracting for the years of my marriage. i won't cite their amount; it was frightful. i was bound up in an inextricable toil of bills and debts, or mortgages and insurances, and all the horrible evils attendant upon them.}
